# vImageCVImageFormat.Format.format14Bayer_GRBG

**Case**

A little-endian 14-bit Bayer pixel format with even rows ordered green-red and odd rows ordered blue-green.

## Declaration

```swift
case format14Bayer_GRBG
```

## Bayer format constants

- **vImageCVImageFormat.Format.format14Bayer_BGGR**: A little-endian 14-bit Bayer pixel format with even rows ordered blue-green and odd rows ordered green-red.
- **vImageCVImageFormat.Format.format14Bayer_GBRG**: A little-endian 14-bit Bayer pixel format with even rows ordered green-blue and odd rows ordered red-green.
- **vImageCVImageFormat.Format.format14Bayer_RGGB**: A little-endian 14-bit Bayer pixel format with even rows ordered red-green and odd rows ordered green-blue.
